name: Kylo drank the vaporwave kool-aid
description:
Maybe he watched Tron one too many times. Maybe Kylo just likes the unique combination of warm and cool colors. Or maybe he was put there by someone, like some kind of hipster detention. 

I shot this at the request of the one person who responded when I asked for requests. "Do it with a lightsaber" they said. So I did. And I also "did."
